Circular "flower" has fringed outer edge and black blobs pointing inwards defining (four?) reserved petals; a small ring or blob in field at top left of panel. On interior, bottom of black band visible at top edge (inside neck painted?). D 34 (top) 45 (bottom) 55?(belly?)
